cs.DB, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SE, cs.PL. 

This paper presents a system for cross-platform data processing, which involves database management, distributed computing, and software engineering. Therefore, cs.DB (Database), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the optimization of tasks and the execution of tasks over different platforms, which are related to cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
